  "prompt": "Are Quora blog posts ever published on media sites, or just Quora answers?",
  "response": "Quora primarily features user-generated content in the form of answers to questions, but it also allows users to create blog posts. While most of the content that gets shared on external media sites tends to be Quora answers, some blog posts may also be picked up or referenced by media outlets, especially if they are particularly insightful or relevant to current events or trending topics. However, the practice of publishing Quora blog posts on media sites is less common compared to answers.",
